    <PrimAttribute name="ignoreTIsAlreadyOnsite" id="ff93b83e-f9f7-4f08-8795-682c0e8566c5">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Boolean"/>
        <text>
Used when confirming wagons and TIs from the rail hand held confirmation
screens for Gdansk. In this situation we don't care if the TIs already exist 
onsite or as a prenote - sometimes they will, most of the time they'll
be new TIs.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
